<varlistentry id="options.UseCurrentViewport">
	<term>UseCurrentViewport</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>AfterStep will treat an application as if it is relative to the current viewport's origin, when that application specifies its geometry at the time of mapping.</para>
		<para>See Also: UseAnyViewport.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
